sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User (Student/Admin)
    participant AuthUI as Auth UI
    participant System
    participant Database

    Note over User,AuthUI: UC-02: Login

    User->>AuthUI: Enters email & password
    AuthUI->>System: login(email, password)
    System->>Database: checkLockStatus(email)
    Database-->>System: lock status

    alt Account is Locked
        System-->>AuthUI: Error: "Account Locked (Too many attempts)"
        AuthUI-->>User: Notify: Account locked
    else Account Active
        System->>Database: validateCredentials(email, hash(password))
        Database-->>System: credentials valid?

        alt Invalid Credentials
            System-->>AuthUI: Error: "Invalid email or password"
            AuthUI-->>User: Prompt to retry login
        else Credentials Valid
            System->>System: Create authenticated session
            System->>Database: getUserRole(email)
            Database-->>System: role

            alt Role: Student
                System-->>AuthUI: Login Success (Student)
                AuthUI-->>User: Redirect to Student Dashboard
            else Role: Admin
                System-->>AuthUI: Login Success (Admin)
                AuthUI-->>User: Redirect to Admin Dashboard
            end
        end
    end